## 7. Insight Cards (Most Important Component)

Insight cards are the **centerpiece of the product**.

### Structure

```
[ Title ]               [ Confidence % ]
[ Description ]
[ Why this matters ]    (expandable)
[ Suggested action ]    (optional)
```

### Visual Rules

* Confidence shown as **text badge**, not a progress bar
* Reasoning is muted and expandable
* Priority is implied by ordering, not color

Example badge:

```
text-xs px-2 py-1
border border-border
rounded-full
text-textSecondary
```

